videos.headline: Iowa continues tradition with children's hospital wave
videos.description: At the end of the first quarter of every Iowa home game, all of the fans, players and coaches wave to the patients at the children's hospital next to the stadium.

videos.headline: Iowa recovers Maryland fumble for TD
videos.description: Iowa recovers a Maryland fumble that rolls all the way to the end zone for a defensive touchdown.
